description:
Big thank you to Q for mentioning my last video!!!!!! And also a big hello to my new subscribers. I thought this Q drop from yesterday was really important - especially for those who are new to the movement - so I decided to quickly narrate / edit it for you guys. This could be a good video to introduce your friends or family to Q (along with videos by Joe M). You can also go to Qmap.pub to see the posts/proofs for yourself & read along to this video if you'd like. And lastly, I want to say thanQ to all my patrons for all of their incredible support. I can't do this without you guys. WE are the news now! Where We Go One We Go All.

Patreon.com/E4L
#WWG1WGA #DarkToLight #TheGreatAwakening #GodWins
